 rience and their children a relevant High Holy Days experience. The service
  includes meaningful High Holy Days liturgy\, music\, Torah and haftarah\, 
 and a sermon. This service is for PTBE members only. We welcome you to join
  PTBE. Contact COO\, Blair Brown at bbrown@ptbe.org.
